text: Lönsboda GoIF is a sports club in Lönsboda in Sweden. It was established on 24 September 1930 as a merger out of Lönsboda IF, Lönsboda GF, Lönsboda CK and Lönsboda Pingpongklubb. The women's soccer team played five seasons in the Swedish top division between 1978-1982. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1930 establishments in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs
